title: #150: Door Guy 3 (@DanishAndOneill)
itunes:title: Door Guy 3 with Danish & O'Neill
description: Jeff Danis and Ryan Oneill met me at the Comedy Store on a beautiful January day. We talked about working as an employee at the Store. It's a job a lot of us had and each era of door guy was different. This is about all the different positions we all worked in while we started comedy.
